          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1717760987384-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>honey sesame chicken skewers </strong>over the <strong>cooked rice </strong>with the <strong>spicy smashed cucumber salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>remaining sesame marinade</strong> all over the chicken and rice</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Serve the cucumber and pepper batons to the side with a dollop of the remaining mayo</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
